title: Fainting Story
description:
Dr. Kirk tells his epic story about fainting at Mardi Gras and discusses vasovagal syncope. (Intro)

The full episode is available for patrons of the podcast.

Become a patron of our podcast by going to https://www.patreon.com/PsychologyInSeattle
